{"tid":597126,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單評價港燈業績","createTime":"2018-03-18T10:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T01:09:29.000Z","uid":34522,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a902250c7ce3afd998fb85e811a2b51791c86b2c","tid":597126,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"上一次就講過港鐵業績﹐今次就分享另一間﹐港燈<br />\n<br />\n我個Blog<br />\n<a href=\"https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F90earndividend.blogspot.com%2F&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=08d7f0a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單評價港燈業績<br />\n<a href=\"https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/blog-post_18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F90earndividend.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F03%2Fblog-post_18.html&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=c63eb2be\" target=\"_blank\">https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/blog-post_18.html</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄部分<br />\n收入<br />\n<br />\n收入係17年就上升左2.4%﹐增幅就比16年增長大左0.5個百分點(無錯﹐係要用埋小數點......)。<br />\n<br />\n港燈的業務咁簡單﹐也都令到增加收入的方法好簡單﹐一係加電費﹐一係增加售電量。但好可惜的係第二個方法並唔可行...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港燈係業績一邊指出用電需求上升﹐但又同時指出售電量比16年少﹐而且預計未來的用電量會繼續跌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近年售電量下跌主要係黎自商業部分﹐相信同近年唔少商廈都了解到節能對於支出的正面影響<br />\n(來源: 港燈2016年年報 連結)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以增加收入方法就係加價﹐而港燈就已經公佈18年總電費會比17年增加2.1仙至112.5仙。無論係港燈定係對面海的中電﹐電費價格都係受政府的監管﹐所以加價能力唔會好似另外一間公用公司煤氣咁&quot;&quot;理論上&quot;&quot;可以隨意加價<br />\n<br />\n溢利<br />\n<br />\n可以見得到係支出方面無咩大的變化﹐最終去到最低的稅後溢利比16年升左6.25%。但係相信大家都仲見到有多一行叫做&quot;&quot;按管制計劃調撥&quot;&quot;﹐呢行就姐係經常係電視聽到的&quot;&quot;管制計劃協議&quot;&quot;﹐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單一句就姐係多除少補﹐直至到左個准許利潤。直至2017年准許利潤回報率係9.99%﹐但由2018年起就會降低至8%﹐姐係話會有更多的利潤被迫要搬離公司條數。港燈當然唔會就咁比個利潤咁容易下跌。由於利潤上限係以固定資產價值做分母﹐所以港燈就可以以增加投資去換黎高D的利潤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前的文:<br />\n簡單評價港鐵業績<br />\n<a href=\"https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/blog-post_13.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F90earndividend.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F03%2Fblog-post_13.html&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=c9fd05d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/blog-post_13.html</a><br />\n<br />\n投資產品:ETF<br />\n<a href=\"https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/etf.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F90earndividend.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F03%2Fetf.html&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=0b1f683f\" target=\"_blank\">https://90earndividend.blogspot.com/2018/03/etf.html</a>"},{"pid":"cdf6f7d90d67b1ac0e27badb3e206775bfa04f1e","tid":597126,"uid":77626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"參考價值低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e192b2d27664d3e2007a9d80def81892bfbf9bd3","tid":597126,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf6f7d90d67b1ac0e27badb3e206775bfa04f1e","tid":597126,"uid":77626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"參考價值低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"文章入面有講到將來的盈利情況同埋酒店計劃"},{"pid":"edb531a85fe7f2665f1cf81d73fba26d8697cab2","tid":597126,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"個酒店係鴨脷洲起,大把人反對<br />\n起唔起得成都未知"},{"pid":"8fcb2abf7f3429618767febec6e2afcb5788dde8","tid":597126,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edb531a85fe7f2665f1cf81d73fba26d8697cab2","tid":597126,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"個酒店係鴨脷洲起,大把人反對<br />\n起唔起得成都未知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"城規早前已經批准起﹐只係問題係起幾多酒店房<br />\n同埋已經出左補地價﹐應該唔會有大問題"},{"pid":"6db97cdeb926d13e7abbdfb89b70bf710b015ede","tid":597126,"uid":1060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-